org.wildfly.swarm.config.messaging.activemq.server

Class Divert<T extends Divert<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wildfly.swarm.config.messaging.activemq.server.Divert<T>

  • public class Divert<T extends Divert<T>>
extends Object
    A messaging resource that allows you to transparently divert messages routed to one address to some other address, without making any changes to any client application logic.
